fields.name: AgentPoolId
fields.description: The resource ID of the agent pool that this node belongs to. This value is not represented on control plane nodes.

fields.name: AvailabilityZone
fields.description: The availability zone this node is running within.

fields.name: BareMetalMachineId
fields.description: The resource ID of the bare metal machine that hosts this node.

fields.name: CpuCores
fields.description: The number of CPU cores configured for this node, derived from the VM SKU specified.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The detailed state of this node.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: DiskSizeGB
fields.description: The size of the disk configured for this node.

fields.name: Image
fields.description: The machine image used to deploy this node.

fields.name: KubernetesVersion
fields.description: The currently running version of Kubernetes and bundled features running on this node.

fields.name: Labels
fields.description: The list of labels on this node that have been assigned to the agent pool containing this node.

fields.name: MemorySizeGB
fields.description: The amount of memory configured for this node, derived from the vm SKU specified.

fields.name: Mode
fields.description: The mode of the agent pool containing this node. Not applicable for control plane nodes.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: The name of this node, as realized in the Kubernetes cluster.

fields.name: NetworkAttachments
fields.description: The NetworkAttachments made to this node.

fields.name: PowerState
fields.description: The power state of this node.

fields.name: Role
fields.description: The role of this node in the cluster.

fields.name: Taints
fields.description: The list of taints that have been assigned to the agent pool containing this node.

fields.name: VMSkuName
fields.description: The VM SKU name that was used to create this cluster node.
